    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no scratches, dents, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin smells new, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, it is perfect, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with all records available; it drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
