    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy. The engine currently runs roughly, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping, indicating the need for a major overhaul or replacement. The body shows visible rust, several dents, and the interior has significant wear and tear, including torn upholstery and non-functioning electronics. This is being sold as-is, ideally for someone looking for a parts car or a dedicated restoration project.",
